summary: This is an email from January 14, 2021, in which an individual forwards flight records (1991-2006) received from counsel for David Rodgers. The sender notes they have not yet reviewed the records but is passing them along immediately.

persons.name: David Rodgers
persons.role: Individual whose counsel provided flight records
persons.context: His legal counsel sent flight records covering 1991-2006 to the email sender.

events.title: Flight Records Provided
events.description: Counsel for David Rodgers sends flight records covering 1991-2006 to the email sender.

keyFacts: Flight records for the period 1991-2006 were provided by counsel for David Rodgers.
The records were sent via email on January 14, 2021.
The sender had not yet reviewed the flight records at the time of the email.
